<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ABR-RUSSIA-BITTER-CAPITALISM-1STLD-440&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GLOOM DESCENDS ON RUSSIANS AS HOPES OF QUICK CAPITALISM FADE 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (SUBS 2nd graf to correct Parliament vote to last month. No other
changes.)  (EDS: A full-length version of this story,
RUSSIA-BITTER-CAPITALISM, has also been transmitted.) 
(js) 
 By MICHAEL R. GORDON and CELESTINE BOHLEN    
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
