<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-02 19:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5496 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SENATE-IMPEACH-BOS &LR;      01-02 0853
